settings.label: Trunks

settings.heading: What you wear below the belt matters!
The pouch is a palace for your phallus®

settings.text:
We invented a unique ergonomic pouch to treat your crown jewels like royalty!

The upper pouch functions as quick-draw access while the lower pouch is made of high-performance mesh fabric to wick away sweat and create more air flow down under.

settings.heading: Made from wood for your wood

settings.text: Our fabric is made from soft cellulosic fibre sourced from sustainable Austrian beech trees. Our products are made in a non-toxic and renewable manufacturing process for your peace of mind.

settings.title: Boxer Briefs
settings.description: Our boxer briefs treat your crown jewels like royalty. There are two ergonomic designs to give ultimate comfort and to eliminate sweat down under.

settings.title: Trunks
settings.description: Our latest trunks are made from exclusive and sustainable MicroModal Air fibres. They're a best fit for men who like ultra comfort with shorter legs.

settings.title: Briefs
settings.description: Streamlined for free motion. These briefs are a best fit for those who want complete freedom and boast ventilated back panels with an absorbent pouch lining.
